name: With My Hands Lifted Up
chorusText:
With my hands lifted up
And my mouth filled with praise
With a heart of thanksgiving
I will praise Thee, o Lord
I will praise Thee, o Lord
I will praise Thee, o Lord
With a heart of thanksgiving
I will praise Thee, o Lord
Met my hande omhoog
Met elke klank wat ek sing
Wil ek u kom verhoog en al my lof aan u bring
Want U is my Skepper, U is my Vriend
Die heem’le lig U omhoog
U word vir ewig vereer
Aan my Koning my Heer, ja my Jesus wat leef
Ons wil U net prys, Heer, ons wil U net prys
